Baby powders are used to absorb excess moisture from the skin and to make the infant’s skin feel refreshed. The Johnson’s Baby Powder is a mild and skin friendly powder formulated especially to suit infants' fragile skin. This Baby Powder from Johnson’s is clinically proven to be safe and tender on your little one’s skin.

After applying the Baby Powder the tiny tot’s skin feels soft and refreshed. It will help removing friction that can arise on the skin due to excess moisture. Such friction can cause bruises on the skin. The dermatologist and allergy tested Johnson’s Baby Powder contains many smooth and slippery particles that slide over one another and help in relieving friction. A lovely and classic scent will linger on your baby’s body after the application of the Johnson’s Baby Powder.

You can use this Baby Powder any time; after bathing
